import java.util.concurrent.*;

class ThreadPoolDemo
{
    public static void main(String[] args)
    {
        ExecutorService pool = Executors.newCachedThreadPool();
        MyTask t1 = new MyTask(5);
        MyTask t2 = new MyTask(7);
        MyTask t3 = new MyTask(8);
        pool.execute(t1);
        pool.execute(t2);
        pool.execute(t3);
        pool.shutdown();
    }
}
class MyTask implements Runnable
{
    int n=10;
    public MyTask(int n){ this.n=n;}
    public void run(){
        for(int i=0;i<n; i++)System.out.print(i); // 01234560123401234567
    }
}

import java.util.*;
class TimerTest {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Timer timer = new Timer("display");
        TimerTask task = new MyTask();
        timer.schedule( task, 1000, 1000 );
    }
}
class MyTask extends TimerTask{
    int n = 0;
    public void run(){
        n++;
        System.out.print( new Date() );
        System.out.println( "---" + n );
    }
}

import javax.swing.*;

class TimerSwing extends JFrame
{
    Timer timer;
    public void init()
    {
        setLayout(null);
        setSize(400,100);
        setDefaultCloseOperation(EXIT_ON_CLOSE);
        setVisible(true);

        timer = new Timer(1000, (e)->{
            setTitle( new java.util.Date().toString());
        });
        timer.start();
    }

    public static void main(String[] args)
    {
        new TimerSwing().init();
    }
}
